wpt.name: GC2NGM6
wpt.desc: 6 of 1 by GeoGirls of Chesco, Unknown Cache (1.5/1.5)

groundspeak:cache.groundspeak:name: 6 of 1
groundspeak:cache.groundspeak:short_description: The cache and log are not at the posted coordinates. You must sign the OFFICIAL LOG sheet to claim this cache. NO replacement logs allowed.
groundspeak:cache.groundspeak:long_description:
"Six of one, half dozen of the other", that is what one GeoGirl said when they were deciding on where to hide a new cache.

"These types of hides are a dime a dozen" chimed in another GeoGirl.

"Yeah, it's a toss up!"

"It is what it is." But where is it? It's anyone's call!

The GeoGirls are full of idioms. What's your favorite saying? Let us know in your log.

At each of the given waypoints, you will find a container - but only one contains the OFFICIAL 6 of 1 LOG sheet. You must find and sign that log!

Remember:"If at first you don't succeed, try, try again".

As a wise elder once said, "Do or do not, there is no try".

groundspeak:log.groundspeak:text: Quick find with dawnie22, 19acassel and our youngest daughter. TFTC
